General:
--------

signoff_request.poy script sends out email notifications if a revision is awaiting signoff.

Dir: /data/mta4/CUS/www/Usint/ 
See also: https://cxc.cfa.harvard.edu/mta_days/mta_script_list/USINT/ti_send_sign_off_req.html


Script:
-------
signoff_request_wrap_script
signoff_request_main_script
signoff_request.py

